For Arcade's 7th Anniversary, we have collaborated with five of our #ArcadeInsiders to design five capsule collections, capturing the essence of what makes each of them distinctly individual yet unmistakably Arcade.

A minimalist at heart who prefers a monochromatic palette, Olivia (@elkantlers) is also big on the little details. Her collection with Arcade focuses on elevated everyday styles that each have their own unique flair, and can all come together to create a polished wardrobe that hits the spot.
